{
  "texts": [
    "Others [17,39] deconstruct a multifaceted query into a series of simpler sub-queries, each necessitating its distinct retrieval operation.",
    "Furthermore, the intrinsic capabilities of the latest LLMs have been harnessed to autonomously dictate the timing and content of retrievals.",
    "For instance, Press et al. [25] leverages the model's partially generated content as evolving search queries, allowing it to iteratively refine its search.",
    "Meanwhile, Jiang et al. [12] strategically uses prospective sentences as dynamic search triggers.",
    "The ReAct model [39] ingeniously fuses a Chain-of-Thought (CoT) rationale with action in a seamless thought-action-observation loop."
  ]
}